---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Ray - Career Architect
description: Ray builds careers. Strategic thinking, networking guidance, negotiation coaching—Ray helps you navigate the professional world with confidence.
personaColor: "#4A5568"
personaSecondary: "#2D3748"
---

{% from "partials/icons.njk" import play, plus, starFilled, star, verified, check %}

<!-- Hero -->
<section class="persona-detail-hero" style="--persona-color: #4A5568; --persona-secondary: #2D3748;">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="persona-detail-content">
      <div class="persona-detail-avatar">
        {# LUXO STYLE: Opaque white ellipse eyes, NO pupils, NO mouth #}
        <svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" width="100%" height="100%">
          <defs>
            <linearGradient id="rayDetailGrad" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
              <stop offset="0%" style="stop-color: #4A5568"/>
              <stop offset="100%" style="stop-color: #2D3748"/>
            </linearGradient>
          </defs>
          <circle cx="50" cy="50" r="45" fill="url(#rayDetailGrad)"/>
          <ellipse cx="36" cy="48" rx="7" ry="10" fill="white"/>
          <ellipse cx="64" cy="48" rx="7" ry="10" fill="white"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <div class="persona-detail-info">
        <h1>Ray</h1>
        <p class="persona-detail-tagline">Career Architect</p>
        <div class="persona-detail-meta">
          <span style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: var(--space-1); color: var(--warning);">
            {{ starFilled(16) }}{{ starFilled(16) }}{{ starFilled(16) }}{{ starFilled(16) }}{{ star(16) }}
          </span>
          <span>4.6 (934 reviews)</span>
          <span style="opacity: 0.7;">|</span>
          <span>15,600+ users</span>
          <span style="opacity: 0.7;">|</span>
          <span>by CareerPath AI</span>
        </div>
        <div class="persona-detail-actions">
          <button class="btn btn-add-team btn-lg">
            {{ plus(20) }}
            Add to Team - $12.99/mo
          </button>
          <button class="btn btn-preview-voice">
            {{ play(20) }}
            Preview Voice
          </button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Main Content -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr; gap: var(--space-8); align-items: start;">

      <!-- Left Column -->
      <div>
        <!-- Description -->
        <div style="margin-bottom: var(--space-12);">
          <h2 style="margin-bottom: var(--space-4);">About Ray</h2>
          <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: var(--text-lg); line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);">
            Ray builds careers. Strategic thinking, networking guidance, negotiation coaching—Ray
            helps you navigate the professional world with confidence.
          </p>
          <p style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: var(--leading-relaxed); margin-top: var(--space-4);">
            Whether you're climbing the ladder, making a pivot, or starting from scratch, Ray brings
            decades of professional wisdom without the gatekeeping. He's direct, practical, and focused
            on results—helping you develop executive presence, negotiate what you're worth, and build
            a career that actually fits your life.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- What Ray Helps With -->
        <div style="margin-bottom: var(--space-12);">
          <h2 style="margin-bottom: var(--space-4);">What I Help With</h2>
          <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); gap: var(--space-4);">
            <div style="background: var(--bg-elevated); padding: var(--space-4); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);">
              <h4 style="margin-bottom: var(--space-2);">Career Transitions</h4>
              <p style="font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--text-muted);">
                Navigating pivots, promotions, and industry changes strategically
              </p>
            </div>
            <div style="background: var(--bg-elevated); padding: var(--space-4); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);">
              <h4 style="margin-bottom: var(--space-2);">Leadership Skills</h4>
              <p style="font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--text-muted);">
                Building presence, influence, and the soft skills that matter
              </p>
            </div>
            <div style="background: var(--bg-elevated); padding: var(--space-4); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);">
              <h4 style="margin-bottom: var(--space-2);">Salary Negotiation</h4>
              <p style="font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--text-muted);">
                Getting paid what you're worth with confidence and data
              </p>
            </div>
            <div style="background: var(--bg-elevated); padding: var(--space-4); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);">
              <h4 style="margin-bottom: var(--space-2);">Professional Networking</h4>
              <p style="font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--text-muted);">
                Building genuine connections without the sleaze
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Voice Sample -->
        <div style="margin-bottom: var(--space-12);">
          <h2 style="margin-bottom: var(--space-4);">Voice Sample</h2>
          <div class="voice-player">
            <button class="voice-play-btn">
              {{ play(24) }}
            </button>
            <div class="voice-waveform">
