              </svg>
            </div>
            <span class="voice-duration">0:25</span>
          </div>
          <p style="font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: var(--space-3); font-style: italic;">
            "Here's the thing about negotiation—most people leave money on the table because they're
            afraid to ask. Let's practice. I'll be the hiring manager. Tell me why you deserve more
            than their initial offer."
          </p>
